where Pa is the apparent permeability coefficient (cm/s), VD and VA are the volumes in the donor (0.15 cm3) and acceptor phase (0.3 cm3), A is the filter area (0.24 cm2), t is the incubation time (14400 s) and \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
